1.6.0.name: wordpress/statpress-community-formerly-statcomm
1.6.0.description:
StatComm provides Realtime Statistics on your blog, collecting information about visitors, spiders, search keywords, feeds, browsers, OS and more. Once the plugin has been activated, it will immediately starts collecting information. StatComm provides many views to analyze the incoming users on your blog, and also spy tools to find out their procedence. For users of other StatPress plugins variations, it provides a well known feature set and information.

We really appreciate your opinion on this plugin. Please vote it or even better, make a donation. All the money is used to support other projects which made Statcomm possible.

Drop a note on the forum(s) about what would you like to be improved/fixed.

Current version includes:

  • Instant user information + Googl
